Cloud computing is a new trend in IT development, deployment and delivery module of business. 
Product and services are provided over internet which are been used by realtime user.
Salesforce is cloud computing technology.
CRM is stands for Customer Relationship Management.
CRM comes under Software as service(Saas).
It is used to increase revenue and profit of organization and businesses by using CRM software.
Their are many CRM software which are:
Salesforce CRM
SAP CRM
Oracle Sales Cloud CRM(Fusion CRM)
Sage CRM
Oracle CRM
Sugar CRM
Netsuit CRM
Oracle on demand CRM
Nimble
